      <t>&lt;p&gt;The BSD Syslog Protocol describes a number of service options related to propagating event messages.  This memo describes two mappings of the syslog protocol to TCP connections, both useful for reliable delivery of event messages. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
